{"tid":328152,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解冇人信我講嘢","createTime":"2017-07-19T11:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T14:23:51.000Z","uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ca601a71d5457f2dab0dbf76633a48fe887189f","tid":328152,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:10:22.000Z","msg":"我一同我屋企人，我身邊啲朋友講話懷疑自己係自閉，有亞氏保加症徵狀會冇人信我嘅😔<br />\n我真係有問題嫁<br />\n我真係蠢過人嫁<br />\n點解你地唔信我姐"},{"pid":"a93b118f8830038fa0333bb50ea963129ced3d22","tid":328152,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:14:26.000Z","msg":"我要做正常人呀<br />\n我要做自己想做嘅嘢呀，屌<br />\n我唔撚想做自閉仔呀仆街<br />\n點解個天要咁對我呀<br />\n我唔要呀<br />\n我唔要做嵯自閉呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649c3e30a6ea55965d351bbc1d1eaf37a10478ff","tid":328152,"uid":99364,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:14:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d120a70ab2e41b577f9e31f123ca4e12a7fdd06","tid":328152,"uid":99364,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:14:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b482205bde6244b5b1f79f57430f8d697677422","tid":328152,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你嗡乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解冇人信我有自閉<br />\n我又唔想做自閉<br />\n有冇人可以救吓我"},{"pid":"b392c4055d36b1b94ae59a7bf1c2b51521c04728","tid":328152,"uid":36478,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:19:25.000Z","msg":"有病大哂?"},{"pid":"867d15c847ade314bd56991a434deff25ded36a9","tid":328152,"uid":81190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有病大哂?</blockquote><br />\n冇話大曬woo"},{"pid":"32b6756890d7184f29a61676cfe2a6dd22fb17cf","tid":328152,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:21:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c7fc